content: 9  /  21   This is a big rival. And it doesn't make a difference who's playing well and who's the better team because anybody can win. We're the better team and we're probably the more skilled team, but they play us tough. They test us and they always challenge us.	by Bussy Adam Found in Miscellaneous Quotes, Share to:
